\c 54 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 54\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Kadhata Nama Rakkina Keessa Jiruu (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; mi'a ribuu qabuun faarfatame; mararoo Daawit isa yeroo warri Ziif dhaqanii, "Daawit nu bira dhokatee jira" jedhanii Saa'olitti himan faarfatamee dha)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, maqaa keetiin ati na oolchi, aangoo keetiinis dhugaa anaaf baasi!
\m \bd 2\bd* Kadhata koo dhaga'i, yaa Waaqayyo, dubbii ani afaan kootiin sitti himadhus dhaggeeffadhu.
\m \bd 3\bd* Namoonni ormaa ana irratti ka'aniiru, warri nama sodaachisanis jireenya koo balleessuu in barbaadu; isaan Waaqayyoon of dura hin buufanne. 
\m \bd 4\bd* Kunoo, Waaqayyo gargaaraa koo ti, gooftichi irkisaa jireenya kootii ti.
\m \bd 5\bd* Wanti hamaan warra ija diinummaatiin na ilaalanitti haa deebi'u; ati amanamaa waan taateef isaan fixi!
\m \bd 6\bd* Ani jaalala kootiin aarsaa siif nan dhi'eessa, yaa gooftaa, ani maqaa kee isa gaariidhaaf galata nan galcha.
\m \bd 7\bd* Ati rakkina hundumaa keessaa waan na baafteef, iji koo gammachuudhaan diinota koo of jalatti in ilaala. 
\b 
